; FILED: multi-list map is correct under vm-src (eshkol-vm-standalone f.esk)
; but the --profile hosted-vm --emit-eskb route drops the second list —
; the exact bug vm_prelude_source.h was created to kill; the ESKB route
; appears to bake in a stale prelude (vm_prelude_cache.h not regenerated).
; native -r : (11 22 33)
